所有已实现的接口：
DataCenterFactory
public class LoadBalanceFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataCenterFactory

This class implements the interface DataCenterFactory, that is to say, LoadBalanceFactory would follow the defined processes of scheduling. While for the instance of LoadBalanceFactory, it can produce different composition for different requests creating approaches, scheduling algorithms, comparison indices.
